      ],
      "content": "The hill rises ahead of you, scrub grass and red dirt, the kind of slope you climb without thinking. Niterói spreads below — rooftops, water towers, the bay going silver in the late afternoon light. You have been here before, on a different day, for a different reason.\n\nYou came by bus. Manoel and Miguel came by bus three days ago. You missed that bus. You have been telling yourself that ever since.\n\nA path climbs upward through the grass."
    },
