        ],
        [
          "noun",
          "towers",
          "radio towers",
          "antennae",
          "antenna"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "Three steel towers, older than they look. They transmit something — you have never been sure what. Miguel once said that radio waves pass through everything. Through walls, through bone. Through whatever it is you are when you are not a body. He said it like it was good news."
    },
