      "content": "Both watches. Removed and bagged before the end — that detail has stayed with you since you heard it. Why bag your watch? To keep it safe. To protect it from whatever you were expecting to happen to the rest of you.\n\nManoel's shows 18:04. Miguel's shows 18:04. Both stopped at the same moment.\n\nYou check your own wrist. Your watch still runs. It reads {{watch}} minutes until dark."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
        [
