        ],
        [
          "noun",
          "bottle",
          "water bottle"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "Empty. They bought it at the bar in Niterói, the same bar where the waitress noticed Miguel checking his watch. A single bottle for two men. That has always seemed to Sergio like the kind of detail that means something, though he has never been able to say what."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
        [
          "d",
