        ],
        [
          "noun",
          "note",
          "notebook",
          "page",
          "notebook page",
          "instruction",
          "instructions"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "A single page, handwritten in clumsy Portuguese. You have seen this before — a copy was sent to all three of you.\n\n*16:30 — estar no local combinado.*\n*18:30 — ingerir as cápsulas, após o efeito proteger os metais aguardar o sinal máscara.*\n\n*16:30 — be at the agreed place.*\n*18:30 — ingest capsules, after effect protect metals await signal mask.*\n\nThat is all. That is the entire instruction. You have read it perhaps two hundred times and it has never become less strange."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
        [
          "d",
          "vintem:feature:shortwave"
