          "Shortwave Radio"
        ],
        [
          "noun",
          "shortwave",
          "radio",
          "receiver"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "Miguel's shortwave, a Motorola he rebuilt from salvage parts. It is on. The dial is set to a frequency you do not recognise — not a broadcast band, something between stations. The speaker produces a soft, continuous static, regular enough that you keep almost hearing something in it. A pattern. A word. Something on the edge of resolution that never quite arrives."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
        [
          "d",
