      ],
      "content": "The ridge opens the world. Niterói below, the bay beyond it, the far shore where Rio begins. The light is going amber now, the city starting to find its own illumination against the coming dark. Everything below is ordinary. Traffic. Lives. People who do not know what is behind you on this hill.\n\nThe wind is stronger here. It carries the smell of salt and something faintly electrical — the towers, probably. Or something else."
    },
