        [
          "title",
          "The City"
        ],
        [
          "noun",
          "city",
          "niterói",
          "bay",
          "view",
          "lights"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "You and Manoel grew up two streets apart, in a neighbourhood that looked nothing like this. Miguel was from further north. You met at a repair shop, three young men with oscilloscopes and too much time and a shared conviction that the gap between technology and the unknown was narrowing every year.\n\nYou can see Miguel's street from here, if you know where to look. You do. You look."
    },
