      "content": "Two capsules in a folded cloth, sealed with wax. You prepared them yourself. You do not know exactly what is in them — that knowledge came from a source you chose to trust. Whatever they contain is meant to alter the frequency of perception. To make you receivable. That is the word that was used: *receivable.* Like a set, tuned to the right station."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
