      "content": "16:30 — be at the agreed place. 18:30 — ingest capsules, after effect protect metals await signal mask.\n\nThat is all the instruction there was. That is all there needs to be."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
        [
          "d",
          "vintem:place:ending-believer"
        ],
        [
          "t",
          "vintem"
